data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a sought-after community just outside of Tradition, this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom Holiday-built residence offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort. Step inside to discover a spacious den/office area, vinyl flooring, and an abundance of natural light that fills every corner of the home.As you explore further, you'll be delighted by the thoughtful upgrades, including a French drain system, whole-house water filter, and a backup power system for storm readiness. The kitchen features granite countertops, complemented by matching upgrades in the bathrooms. Plus, with solar panels that will be fully paid off by closing, you'll enjoy significantly reduced energy bills. Outside, indulge in the ultimate relaxation with your own private pool, screened porch, and three-car garage with epoxy floors. The lush yard boasts several fruit trees, including papaya, coconut, and mangoes, creating a serene outdoor oasis. A charming pergola and paved pathway add to the allure of the outdoor space, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine.

Located just moments away from Tradition's shopping and dining options, this home offers convenience without the HOA fees. With its immaculate condition and captivating curb appeal, this property is a rare find for those who appreciate quality craftsmanship and outdoor living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
